    "His anti-Renaissance views were criticized in his lifetime by <a href=\"/berensonb\">Bernard Berenson</a> and posthumously by the architectural historian <a href=\"/scottg\">Geoffrey Scott</a>.": [],
    "As a reformer, his book <em>Unto This Last</em> (1860) is said to have influenced Mahatma Gandhi.": [],
